(ns o2w.api.atom
  (:require [o2w.api.impl :as impl]
            [reagent.core :as r]
            [reagent.ratom :refer [IReactiveAtom reaction Reaction]]))

(defprotocol IapiAtom
  (fetch! [this])
  (clean! [this])
  (refresh! [this])
  (ensure! [this cb])
  (loading? [this]))

(defn get-params [{:keys [endpoint params reaction? endpoint-reaction? base-url-reaction? base-url]}]
  (let [base-url (if base-url-reaction? @base-url base-url)]
    (cond-> {:params (if reaction? @params params)}
      base-url (assoc :base-url base-url))))

(defn ->endpoint [{:keys [endpoint endpoint-reaction?]}] (if endpoint-reaction? @endpoint endpoint))
(defrecord RemoteAtom [this]
  IAtom
  IReactiveAtom

  IapiAtom
  (fetch! [{:keys [model] :as this}]
    (let [extra-params (get-params this)]
      (impl/req (->endpoint this) (merge extra-params {:ok #(reset! model %)}))))

  (refresh! [this] (fetch! this))
  (clean! [{:keys [data? model]}]
    (reset! data? nil)
    (reset! model nil))

  (ensure! [{:keys [model refresh timeout ok error loading? data?] :as args} cb]
    (if @data?
      (do
        (js/console.log "ENSURE " cb)
        (when cb (cb model)))
      (when-not @loading?
        (let [extra-params (get-params args)
              set-timeout! (fn [] (when refresh
                                    (when @timeout (js/clearInterval @timeout))
                                    (reset! timeout (js/setInterval #(refresh! args) (* 1000 refresh)))))]
          (set-timeout!)
          (reset! loading? true)
          (impl/req (->endpoint args)
                    (merge args
                           extra-params
                           {:ok    #(do
                                      (reset! data? true)
                                      (reset! model %)
                                      (reset! loading? false)
                                      (when cb (cb model))
                                      (when ok (ok % model)))
                            :error #(do
                                      (reset! data? true)
                                      (reset! model nil)
                                      (reset! loading? false)
                                      (when error (error % model)))}))))))
  (loading? [{:keys [loading?]}]
    @loading?)

  cljs.core/IDeref
  (-deref [{:keys [model data?] :as this}]
    @(reaction (when-not @data? (ensure! this nil)))
    @model)

  cljs.core/ISwap
  (-swap! [this f x]
    (ensure! this (fn [model] (swap! model f x))))
  (-swap! [this f x y]
    (ensure! this (fn [model] (swap! model f x y))))
  (-swap! [this f x y more]
    (ensure! this (fn [model] (apply swap! model f (into [x y] more)))))

  cljs.core/IReset
  (-reset! [{:keys [model]} data]
    (reset! model data)))

(defn remote-atom [endpoint & {:keys [initial params base-url] :as args}]
  (let [model              (r/atom initial)
        data?              (r/atom false)
        loading?           (r/atom false)
        timeout            (r/atom nil)
        reaction?          (= (type params) Reaction)
        endpoint-reaction? (= (type endpoint) Reaction)
        base-url-reaction? (= (type base-url) Reaction)
        this               (map->RemoteAtom (merge args {:endpoint           endpoint
                                                         :endpoint-reaction? endpoint-reaction?
                                                         :base-url-reaction? base-url-reaction?
                                                         :timeout            timeout
                                                         :loading?           loading?
                                                         :data?              data?
                                                         :params             params
                                                         :reaction?          reaction?
                                                         :model              model}))]

    (when reaction? (r/track! (fn [] (reset! data? false) @params)))
    (when endpoint-reaction? (r/track! (fn [] (reset! data? false) @endpoint)))
    (when base-url-reaction? (r/track! (fn [] (reset! data? false) @base-url)))

    this))
